7 SECTION 2. EMERGENCY CLAUSE. It is found and determined by the
8 General Assembly of the State of Arkansas that the operations of a state
9 public retirement system are complex; that the Arkansas Teacher Retirement
10 System must be able to meet the needs of its members as anticipated by the
11 General Assembly; that certain provisions of the Arkansas Teacher Retirement
12 System Act, ยง 24-7-201 et seq., need immediate revision and updating to
13 address administrative complexities caused by these provisions and to bring
