15 actuarial requirements; that the revisions and updates are of great
16 importance to members of the Arkansas Teacher Retirement System and to other
17 citizens of the State of Arkansas; that as the Arkansas Teacher Retirement
18 System operates on a fiscal year of July 1 to June 30, an effective date of
19 July 1, 2025, is necessary in order to allow the provisions within this act
20 to begin on the first day of the fiscal year and to allow for a structured
